1)Enable session middleware
2)Add session service with the required settings
3)Upon successful login store employee's email in to session and redirect employee/index and the welcome <email> should be displayed on top right corner of home page
4)Provide logout feature, when the user logs out it should be redirected to login page
5)For anonymous users the employee home page should display brief employee details and a "View Details" link
6)For authenticated users the employee home page should display brief employee details and "Create New Employee", "View Details", "Edit" and "Delete" links should
be displayed
